# Installation Guide

This project is designed for local Windows production.

## Requirements

- Python
- FFmpeg
- n8n
- Wav2Lip
- Edge TTS
- Character images prepared for lip sync

## n8n URL

If n8n runs in Docker, use:

`	ext
http://host.docker.internal:8110/produce-episode
`

If n8n runs directly on Windows, use:

`	ext
http://127.0.0.1:8110/produce-episode
`
